==事發經過==

===劫持===

當時，快桅阿拉巴馬號上有20名船員，載有17,000[[公噸|公噸]]的貨物正前往[[肯亞|肯亞]]的[[蒙巴薩|蒙巴薩]]。船員們都曾在工會培訓學校受過反海盜訓練，並且於前一天還在船上操練過。訓練的內容則包括了使用小型武器、以及教授反恐、基本安全、急救、和其他安全相關的課程。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.motherjones.com/mojo/2009/04/another-miracle-brought-you-americas-unions-time-pirates |title=Another Miracle Brought to You By America's Unions（This Time With Pirates!） {{!}} Mother Jones<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2016-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808232515/http://www.motherjones.com/mojo/2009/04/another-miracle-brought-you-americas-unions-time-pirates |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://blog.aflcio.org/2009/04/08/union-crew-avoids-pirate-takeover-but-ships-captain-held-hostage/ AFL-CIO NOW BLOG | Union Crew Avoids Pirate Takeover, But Ship's Captain Held Hostage<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090414220648/http://blog.aflcio.org/2009/04/08/union-crew-avoids-pirate-takeover-but-ships-captain-held-hostage/ |date=2009-04-14 }}</ref> 2009年4月8日一早，海盜警報器大作，在被劫的台籍漁船{{le|穩發161號|FV Win Far 161}}上有四名海盜對快桅阿拉巴馬號發動了攻擊。<ref>{{cite news|first= Chiang|last= Huang-chih|url= http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/editorials/archives/2009/09/07/2003452966|agency= |newspaper= [[Taipei_Times|Taipei Times]]|date= 2009-09-07|title= Does the Ministry of Foreign Affairs care about 'Win Far'?|accessdate= 2013-10-30|archive-date= 2020-11-28|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201128201940/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/editorials/archives/2009/09/07/2003452966|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name=BBC7989474>{{cite news|title=Somali pirates hijack Danish ship|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7989474.stm|date=2009-04-08|accessdate=2009-04-08|publisher=BBC news|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223180336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7989474.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CNN>{{cite news|title=Ship carrying 20 Americans believed hijacked off Somalia|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/africa/04/08/ship.hijacked/index.html|date=2009-04-09|accessdate=2009-04-09|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207173215/http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/africa/04/08/ship.hijacked/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據當時的美國國防部長[[羅伯特·蓋茨|羅伯特·蓋茨]]說，四名海盜的年齡全都是在17歲到19歲之間。<ref>{{cite news|title=Somalian pirate suspect arrives in New York to be tried in U.S. court|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2009/04/20/us-somaliapirate.html|date=2009-04-20|accessdate=2013-08-12|publisher=CBC News|archive-date=2012-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114015324/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2009/04/20/us-somaliapirate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

